      <h4 class="push-half--bottom">Supported browsers</h4>
      <p>FreeBMD has been tested on most common browsers. We recommend using the latest version of any browser. If you are using a version older than Chrome (v 25), Firefox (v 4.0), Internet Explorer (v 9), Edge, Safari (v 5.1), or Opera (v 15) then you might experience some issues. If you do, we suggest you update to a more recent version.</p>
